news_header: Iceland's PM Kristrún Frostadóttir leads amidst global political challenges.
news_original_title: Islannin uusi pääministeri arvostaa Sanna Marinia – sukkahousujen sijaan hallitus sai lempinimen sotureilta
news_text: Kristrún Frostadóttir, Iceland's 36-year-old Prime Minister, leads a women-majority government during global upheaval, focusing on everyday life and equality. He emphasizes Iceland's unique geopolitical position, supports Greenland, and advocates for a new EU membership referendum.
